FEATURES

- add non-naive equality
- add hashcode

PERFORMANCE

- precompute size in each operation
- migrate to bitsets + arrays instead of mutable maps for SubMap nodes
- have a specialized _insertWith that takes a key and a value instead of a list
  of key/value pairs.

ABANDONED

- have a specialized leaf node for when there's only one key/value pair: tried,
  no noticeable improvement
- have a specialized _insertWith for when the combine function is (x,y) => x:
  tried, no noticeable improvement
